Subject: Re: [T2] valve slapping or stuck lifter

That's a sticking lifter that needs to pump up. It may do it on its
own after a minute or two. For stubborn cases a bottle of Valve Medic
(by Gunk/Solder Seal - available at Napa and many FLAPS) will do the
trick without having to pull the lifter for maintenance.

John

